title: MAR 18 2022 - WAR IN UKRAINE - DAY 23 UPDATE
description:
The New York Times admits that Hunter Biden’s laptop is authentic, thereby completely rejecting previous claims of ‘Russian Disinformation’, updates from the Institute for the Study of War (ISW) reveal most current advances and counter attacks. In a rare public appearance, President Putin addresses the Russian people at a patriotic rally in Moscow on the anniversary of the annexation of Crimea. New statistics reveal that 30% of the Ukrainian refugees are from other countries, and Republicans raise red flags on Biden’s Supreme Court nominee, judge Ketanji Brown Jackson’s prior judicial rulings, specifically on sex offender-related offenses. Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
